This software is created with the intention of pleasing Allah (SWT) and
helping Muslims improve their worship during Ramadan and beyond.

Any rewards (Hasanat) displayed are simulative for motivation purposes.
The actual rewards are known only to Allah (SWT).

"من دعا إلى خير فله مثل أجر فاعله"
"Whoever calls to guidance will have a reward similar to those who follow it"

May Allah accept our efforts and forgive our shortcomings.

